creator: The Trade Labor Marketplace
descriptionHtml:
We started TraLaMa because we believe in the important role skilled tradespeople play in our nation’s economy. From masons to roofers. From framers to painters. From tile installers to electricians. Without these trade laborers, the construction industry (and all of our homes) would crumble.

Until TraLaMa, there was no easy way for trade laborers to connect with potential employers, and no way for companies in the construction trades to connect with skilled laborers.
descriptionShort: The Trade Labor Marketplace is where skilled trade laborers can find work.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Laborer Features: Remember Me, Improved User Dashboard, Example Gallery, License and Insurance, Profile Picture Editing
Business Features: Get Started Added Punch list Items, Public Phone Number, Website, Year Founded, Business Profile Dashboard
General Features: Logout confirmation. When a user taps ‘logout’ they will be asked to confirm the action. Maps are reduced in size to allow users to scroll up and down the page using the sidebar areas.
